src:
【圖多】F奶女星兩條線泳裝險露點　腿抬高高洩「神祕三角洲」
05 Nov 2019, 06:55 by 陳立妍
25歲的F奶寫真女星緒方咲於5年前踏入寫真界，長相甜美的她不僅「胸器」驚人，更擁有一雙85公分的逆天長腿。近日她在IG分享深V辣照，其中一張美腿抬高高的照片，讓「神祕三角地帶」若隱若現，立刻掀起鄉民一陣暴動。


緒方咲在網上公開深V辣照，美腿抬高高「神祕三角地帶」若隱若現。（翻攝自緒方咲IG）

身高168公分的緒方咲腿長85公分，超過身高的一半，得天獨厚的美腿被《 週刊PLAYBOY》選為「美腿橫綱」；前年開始她以美腿照在推特上報時，「腿時計」也成為話題，並獲得「寫真偶像摩天樓」的封號。


緒方咲身材火辣，擁有傲人F罩杯。（翻攝自緒方咲IG）

今年6月底緒方咲發行首本寫真集，F奶、白皙美腿成最大賣點，近日打鐵趁熱推出DVD「Seventh Heaven」，她也賣力在IG狂貼辣照宣傳。


身高168公分的緒方咲卻有85公分的逆天長腿，被封為「美腿橫綱」。（翻攝自緒方咲IG）

除了拍攝花絮照外，緒方咲也時常在社群網站上傳比基尼、cosplay、開岔露乳等各種養眼照，搭配撩人姿勢及眼神，成功吸引28萬名粉絲追縱。


緒方咲常在社群網站分享養眼照，吸引超過28萬網友追蹤。（翻攝自緒方咲IG）

更新時間｜2019.11.05 06:54

[图多]F milk actress two lines swimwear danger dew point legs lift high vent "mysterious delta"
05 Nov 2019, 06:55 by Chen Lizhen
The 25-year-old F milk photo actress Ogata entered the photo world five years ago. She is not only "smart" but also has a pair of 85 cm long legs. Recently, she shared a deep V photo in IG. One of the photos with high legs raised the fascinating "mysterious triangle" and immediately provoked a riot in the villagers.


Sadakata sneaked a deep V on the Internet, and the "mysterious triangle" of the beautiful legs was looming. (Review from Saw square IG)

The 168-cm-tall Ogata is 85 centimeters long, more than half the height. The unique leg is selected as the "Big Legs" by the weekly magazine PLAYBOY. The previous year, when she used the beautiful legs to shine on Twitter, the "leg time meter" also Become a topic and get the title of "Photo Idol Skyscraper".


Ogata is a hot body with a proud F cup. (Review from Saw square IG)

At the end of June this year, Sadawa had released the first photo album. F milk and white 皙 成 became the biggest selling point. Recently, I launched the DVD "Seventh Heaven", and she also worked hard on IG.


Ogata, who is 168 centimeters tall, has a leg of 85 centimeters and is labeled as a "legged leg." (Review from Saw square IG)

In addition to taking pictures, Sakura also frequently uploads various eye-catching photos such as bikini, cosplay, and open breasts on the social networking site. With the gestures and eyes of the deaf, it has successfully attracted 280,000 fans.


Ogata often shares eye-catching photos on social networking sites, attracting more than 280,000 users to follow. (Review from Saw square IG)
